# Privacy Policy

## General Information

The protection of your personal data is very important to me. This app ("Kio-Do") does not store or process any personal data outside your device. No data is transferred to third parties or stored on external servers.

## Data Collection and Storage

All data entered by you (e.g., tasks) is stored locally on your device only. There is no transmission to external servers or third parties.

## External Services

This app does not use any external services (such as Google Analytics, Firebase, or advertising networks) that could collect personal data.

## Permissions

The app requests only the permissions necessary for basic functionality (e.g., local storage).

## Contact

If you have any questions regarding privacy, please contact:  
kiba@kibaofficial.net

## Changes

This privacy policy may be updated in the future. The latest version will always be available at this link.
